tests.game.ai.shared.model

Class TestAbstractBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.game.ai.shared.model.TestAbstractBoard
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestConnect4Board, TestTictactoeBoard

    public abstract class TestAbstractBoard
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an abstract test class that defines some common testing method shared by
    TestConnect4Board and TestTictactoeBoard by using JUnit4 and Mockito
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    btdiem
